	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just an I/O port, Nintendo never used it. AFAIK, only Hacker's Hacker Pro used it for communication with the box.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

